": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Summer_Olympic_Games\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Tonight I think is all about celebrating Kate and that amazing accomplishment,\\\" King said.\", \"from\": 2867, \"to\": 2958, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2909, \"end\": 2913, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kate_Ramsay\", \"score\": 0.9976112521119777, \"rank\": 0.002394457381257174, \"text\": \"Kate\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kate_Ramsay\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kate_Ramsay\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I was actually so far behind, I took a peek up and saw her finish,\\\" King said, with a laugh.\", \"from\": 2960, \"to\": 3053, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Summer McIntosh, of Canada, won yet another gold at the Paris Olympics.\", \"from\": 3055, \"to\": 3126, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3055, \"end\": 3070, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Summer_McIntosh\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Summer McIntosh\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Summer_McIntosh\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Summer_McIntosh\"}, {\"begin\": 3075, \"end\": 3081, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\", \"score\": 0.9982181631419901, \"rank\": 0.0011159788452454425, \"text\": \"Canada\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This time she cruised to victory in the women's 200-meter butterfly final on Thursday.Matthias Schrader/APhide caption  Also on Thursday, Canadian star Summer McIntosh - who trains in the U.S. - swam to another gold in the women's 200 meter butterfly final.\", \"from\": 3127, \"to\": 3384, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"American Regan Smith took silver.\", \"from\": 3385, \"to\": 3418, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3385, \"end\": 3393, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999981619383628, \"rank\": 1.7210641701264976e-06, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 3394, \"end\": 3405, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Regan_Smith\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.7011534346196597e-28, \"text\": \"Regan Smith\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Regan_Smith\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Regan_Smith\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The results so far have beena disappointment for the U.S.American swimmers left the national trials in Indianapolis last monthconfident after posting blazing fast timesand posting new records.\", \"from\": 3420, \"to\": 3612, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3523, \"end\": 3535, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indianapolis\", \"score\": 0.999369829786942, \"rank\": 0.0006253378695289298, \"text\": \"Indianapolis\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indianapolis\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indianapolis\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But so far, despite often swimming personal best times, they have not been fast enough to win against a rising class of international talent.\", \"from\": 3614, \"to\": 3755, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"These Olympics have not been a washout.\", \"from\": 3757, \"to\": 3796, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"American swimmers have notched 20 total medals, four of them gold.\", \"from\": 3798, \"to\": 3864, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3798, \"end\": 3806, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999981619383628, \"rank\": 1.7210641701264976e-06, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But in a typical Summer Games, America's powerhouse team captures ten gold medals.\", \"from\": 3865, \"to\": 3947, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Asked about the U.S. performance with three days of competition still to go, Douglass said the team remains confident.\", \"from\": 3949, \"to\": 4067, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4026, \"end\": 4034, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Frederick_Douglass\", \"score\": 0.9995628180867038, \"rank\": 0.000437373124890394, \"text\": \"Douglass\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Frederick_Douglass\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Frederick_Douglass\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We are proud of ourselves and proud of what we have done,\\\" said Douglass after her gold-medal winning race.\", \"from\": 4069, \"to\": 4177, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4134, \"end\": 4142, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Frederick_Douglass\", \"score\": 0.9995628180867038, \"rank\": 0.000437373124890394, \"text\": \"Douglass\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Frederick_Douglass\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Frederick_Douglass\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We do not listen to all the outside noise, we kind of stick together.\\\"\", \"from\": 4179, \"to\": 4250, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"On Thursday, Chinese swimmers implicated ina doping scandalwon two bronze medals.\", \"from\": 4252, \"to\": 4333, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4265, \"end\": 4272, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9255685586203768, \"rank\": 0.055339630077998435, \"text\": \"Chinese\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Zhang Yufei took bronze in the women's 200-meter butterfly final.\", \"from\": 4335, \"to\": 4400, \"